p.font: The cache IS NOT at listed coordinates! To find the cache you have to figure out puzzle below.

element.long-description:
I've been to Rush many times, mostly looking for geocaches, and that was very enjoyable even when I didn't find any, because this is very nice area. And there has always been the red windsock blowing friendly on the top of high mast. But last month I realized the windsock disappeared... I was very disappointed, so here is the cache to commemorate this windsock.
The listed coordinates are pointing only the general area where the windsock used to be. To find the cache you have to solve the puzzle below:
Enjoy!
